{"tid":2198398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日笑台資，台積電派錢","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T13:19:27.000Z","uid":169310,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a628324d25bb6520f7bbc5684592e05a582732","tid":2198398,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"台積電因應疫情停辦運動會，經費轉贈員工<br />\n.<br />\n台灣的半導體大廠台積電（<a href=\"http://2330.TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2330.TW&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fh5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=ed379689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">2330.TW</a>）今日（11日）宣佈，為避免群聚活動增加疫情感染風險，停辦今年的運動會，不過，原用於舉行運動會的經費，將會轉發給台灣全體員工，每人獲發1000元新台幣面額的商品卡。<br />\n.<br />\n此外，為鼓舞士氣，台積電決定發放特別獎金1.2萬元台幣，據台灣多間傳媒引述台積電表示，獲發特別獎金的合資格員工共有4.2萬名，包括工程師、管理師、行政及技術人員等，相當於獎金金額達到5.04億元新台幣（約1.3億港元）。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我愛台積電！我係台積電人！香港仲成日笑台資，你睇下國泰同賤貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炒賣你啊"},{"pid":"2cf6949e9a37f63c14457183abc8c6948df6f54c","tid":2198398,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c338f4c017d5f3f68c18b0d7a3a42ab54f1afb0","tid":2198398,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d033255c89965570808cccc4e4ec87a80f618906","tid":2198398,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"Tsm tsm tsm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\